Faggot Bruce
[[Image:Faggot_bruce.png|center]]


'''Faggot Bruce''' is the hottest rap sensation to hit the mean streets of the internet since [http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=38_MwcGDNhQ Yo' Momma On Crack Rock]. His lyrical stylings would fall somewhere between black person and [[faggot|Liberace]] if both of them were locked up in a supermax prison and were forced to be cell mates. The resulting [[mpreg]] would roughly approximate Faggot Bruce in lyrical content, "phat" beats, and a penchant for [[anal|buggery]]. Bruce has made a name for himself rapping about all the current issues facing the gay community through the bastard child known as [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Homo_hop homo-hop], focusing on negro prison rape and [http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vjpmxvivlxE ticklin' turds]. What more could you ask for?

==Dats Racys!==

Naturally, Faggot Bruce's rise to internets fame has been marred by h8rs from the rap community. For the most part, this demographic is made up of [[Niggers|prisonbait]] and sexually frustrated [[13 year old boy]]s who are uncomfortable with a strong black man [[rape|tenderly loving]] a white mans corn hole, while they can't even get a crack whore to [[Blowjob|slob their knob]]. Hilarious comments can be found in almost every one of his internet profiles.

